commit.message:
call enableBMFF() to support reading CR3 EXIF files.
Does not harm loading non-CR3 files.

replacing space with "_" in LHDR_VERSION_STR_SUFFIX for build
to work correctly.

Most likely not the correct way to do this.

Fix mac build for packages installed via brew on mac.

Homebrew boost libraries (as found by cmake) are relative symlinks to their
original location.  file(COPY ...) copies the symlinks themselves, as opposed
to the files, with a result of broken relative symlinks.

Also add missing boost atomic library in the build.
fix typo

fix hdrhtml

properly saves images when resize is requested

Fix issue #265: omp crash.

Don't use nestedthreads when threads aren't nested.
Also some more variable renaming for more readable code.

Include cstddef

Solves #260

Implement over-exposure mitigation in Debevec.

Same mechanism as was implemented for Robertson, but we need to derive one global weight for all channels at once. Take the worst case.
This fixes issue #210.
Better variable naming in debevec
